title: Star's Unfinished and Miscellaneous Art!
content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:monotypical]]

[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

Hey, hey, it's me again, Star. I have some drawings that don't quite fit in my character art page, and I have a bunch of unfinished stuff, so here's some of that. You may say, "Star, stop drawing 3/4 view busts," to which I must say that many of these are old.
